<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="verdana, arial"><B>Updated:</B> December 7th 2000</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="verdana, arial">
<P>Here is the information I have so far on the Mage Epic Quest. It is in the order that you should complete it.</P>

<P>The quest starter is in Lake Rathtear. Speak to Rykas (apx loc 1000, -700). He will start you on the path to many quests (and I mean many!) that lead to the final reward. The quest has now been solved, and the reward is the very nice <A HREF="weapon_detail.php3?search=485">Orb of Mastery</A>.You can download a text only version of this quest <A HREF="files/mage_epic_quest_full_12072000.txt">HERE</A> for printing out.</P>
</FONT>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>

